{"tid":513851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"交通黑警電單車「自炒」　復遭私家車撞","createTime":"2017-12-30T03:42:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-30T03:46:08.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a292c0bfc43b5fcb4a7218ae645e4fc01ac4c58c","tid":513851,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T03:42:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171230/s00001/73cd43b1ea3efd75ebd22aa482490c66.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171230%2Fs00001%2F73cd43b1ea3efd75ebd22aa482490c66.jpg&h=8c110e71&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20171230/s00001/73d1542ee6392200028922bda4bad2f3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20171230%2Fs00001%2F73d1542ee6392200028922bda4bad2f3.jpg&h=38e8600f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一輛黑警電單車凌晨1時許沿山道天橋往下山方向行駛，至近干諾道西天橋時失控翻側，交通黑警墮地腰膝受傷，通知同袍到場協助；其後一輛白色私家車從後駛至，撞到電單車後未有停下，反而離開現場。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n交通黑警清醒送院治理，黑警正追查涉事私家車下落。"},{"pid":"45a3dbc1cfc3c861d80eb1c720c68fb819c0469b","tid":513851,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-30T03:46:08.000Z","msg":"weak"}]}